{"tid":1073842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【移交逃犯】美商會對修例「有強烈保留」　憂損港未來及中美關係","createTime":"2019-03-23T03:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T03:43:57.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78c6cad44c78fa79d1d1457255435df39586681f","tid":1073842,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59390153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390153&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1afef0f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390153&h=7c9ad007\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59390153</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190320/large/1553069673_79ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F1553069673_79ee.jpg&h=6c2377c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港美國商會會長早素娜強調修例影響香港未來以至中美關係，甚至是《美國─香港政策法》等，對港人非常重要，要深入了解。<br />\n<br />\n港府建議修改《逃犯條例》和《刑事事宜相互法律協助條例》，容許香港與內地、澳門及台灣等未有簽訂移交逃犯協議地區，以單次個案方式移交逃犯，引起商界憂慮。香港美國商會早前表明對修例「有強烈保留」，該會會長早素娜（Tara Joseph）今日（20日）出席活動時，強調修例影響香港未來以至中美關係，甚至是《美國─香港政策法》等，對港人非常重要，要深入了解。"}]}